len určití študenti, je tak?

527
00:35:59,758 --> 00:36:01,174
Boli to títo študenti?

528
00:36:02,229 --> 00:36:03,298
(Jang Hye Jin,
Kim Hee Kyung, Lee Yoo Ri)

529
00:36:03,298 --> 00:36:06,544
