571
00:38:50,019 --> 00:38:52,094
To medzi tvojím otcom a riaditeľom.

572
00:38:52,448 --> 00:38:54,063
Nevyzerali dvakrát šťastne.

573
00:38:54,388 --> 00:38:55,549
