641
00:44:09,098 --> 00:44:10,769
Oni sú na inej úrovni.

642
00:44:10,769 --> 00:44:12,244
Veď to.

643
00:44:13,169 --> 00:44:14,844
Nič som sa neučil.

644
00:44:19,078 --> 00:44:20,153
Chceš sa pridať ku mne?

645
00:44:22,308 --> 00:44:24,094
- A k čomu?
